            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Mesmo que o array <code>tasks</code> esteja vazio, <code>tasks.length</code> nos dá o número de elementos nele.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" tasks = [];\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(tasks.length);\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"0\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
